snippet.textDisplay: I'm tired of these comments constantly bashing Colton. Colton is such an amazing, talented, and humble guy. First off you Eminem fans need to chill. Unlike Em, Colson actually switches up his music and explores different genres of music like a real artist should to find his or her voice and true potential. Em has stuck to rap for 20 years. Second for those of yall hating for the autotune. When I say EVERY ARTIST I mean EVERY ARTIST uses autotune. There is nothing wrong with it. Finally for those of you saying he needs to work on his range. Colson has naturally a very low voice so range is very difficult for him and if he wants to work on it or change his range in music he will. ITS HIS MUSIC, HIS VOICE, HIS CHOICE. DONT LIKE IT? LEAVE. That simple, that's all.
